videos.headline: Badgers score on 50-yard punt return
videos.description: Cornerback Nick Nelson freezes the Michigan punt team and returns the punt for a touchdown, giving No. 5 Wisconsin a 7-0 lead over No. 24 Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Badgers score on 50-yard punt return) 2017/11/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Peters fumbles reaching for goal line
videos.description: Quarterback Brandon Peters rolls out and reaches for the end zone as the ball comes loose near the Wisconsin goal line. Wisconsin recovers to keep a 7-0 lead over Michigan.

videos.headline: Michigan powers through for tying TD
videos.description: Fullback Ben Mason goes up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown as Michigan ties Wisconsin 7-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan powers through for tying TD) 2017/11/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hornibrook's INT sets up Michigan field goal
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook's pass is intercepted by Devin Bush, setting up a Wolverines field goal to give Michigan a 10-7 lead over Wisconsin.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Hornibrook's INT sets up Michigan field goal) 2017/11/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hornibrook throws 24-yard TD strike to Taylor
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook throws a strike down the middle to WR A.J. Taylor for a 24-yard touchdown, as Wisconsin takes a 14-10 lead over Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Hornibrook throws 24-yard TD strike to Taylor) 2017/11/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Is Wisconsin doing enough to make CFP push?
videos.description: Jonathan Vilma and Chip Kelly hope the CFP committee is paying attention to the undefeated Badgers.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Is Wisconsin doing enough to make CFP push?) 2017/11/18
